00:05:27.487 --> 00:05:29.744
Preterm delivery, perinatal mortality.

124
00:05:29.744 --> 00:05:31.496
The ACOG says all pregnant women

125
00:05:31.496 --> 00:05:34.492
should be screened for anemia, but this is a consensus.

