00:17:39.732 --> 00:17:42.021
at the enrichment level that we do in this country,

369
00:17:42.021 --> 00:17:43.992
most women only get about 240 micrograms

370
00:17:43.992 --> 00:17:45.752
from enriched grains.

371
00:17:45.752 --> 00:17:48.690
That's why you have to be on a multivitamin.

372
00:17:48.690 --> 00:17:52.002
So, you know, childbearing age,

373
00:17:52.002 --> 00:17:55.733
about 12 when sexual activity starts in this country

