00:17:55.733 --> 00:17:59.386
because by 18, 50% of adolescents are sexually active,

375
00:17:59.386 --> 00:18:01.634
up until about 52.

376
00:18:01.634 --> 00:18:03.624
I met a woman a few weeks ago. New patient.

377
00:18:03.624 --> 00:18:06.993
She's 74. Asian American, born in this country.

378
00:18:06.993 --> 00:18:08.857
She was the youngest of eight children.

