00:18:36.502 --> 00:18:39.873
Any of the other AEDs, you get put on 800 per day.

390
00:18:43.770 --> 00:18:47.731
Screening ultrasound, this is done between 16 and 20 weeks

391
00:18:47.731 --> 00:18:50.242
in the absence of a specific indication.

392
00:18:50.242 --> 00:18:53.133
This is what we would call the fetal anatomy survey.

