00:18:53.967 --> 00:18:55.607
You can determine the position,

394
00:18:55.607 --> 00:19:00.483
movement, breathing, heart rate, fetal size, weight,

395
00:19:01.495 --> 00:19:04.380
how much amniotic fluid is there, location of the placenta,

396
00:19:04.380 --> 00:19:06.495
and the number of fetuses, okay?

397
00:19:06.495 --> 00:19:10.136
It's not gonna find major malformay or minor malformations.

398
00:19:10.136 --> 00:19:11.974
It's gonna find major ones,

