00:19:22.920 --> 00:19:24.387
What would you do?

404
00:19:24.387 --> 00:19:25.920
And I understand that argument,

405
00:19:25.920 --> 00:19:28.043
but it's still called a screening ultrasound.

406
00:19:28.984 --> 00:19:33.590
Okay, our next question, 18-year-old G1 P0,

